<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>GetmeMusic Converter</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-container">
        <form action="/convert-mp3" method="POST" id="form">
            <a href="/"><h1><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>Youtube Video to MP3 Converter</h1></a>
            <h4>Place your Video ID here</h4>
            <div>
                <input type="text" name="videoID" placeholder="Video ID/"><button id="convert-btn">Convert</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-container">
        <% if(typeof success != "undefined" && success) { %>
            <div class="success">
                <p><%= song_title %></p>
                <a href="<%= song_link %>"><button id="download-btn">Download</button></a><a href="/"><button class="return-btn">Return</button></a>
            </div>
            <% } else if(typeof success != "undefined" && !success) { %>
                <div class="errors">
                    <p><%= message %></p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="faqsection">
        <ul>
            <h1>What is this App?</h1>
            <p>GetmeMusic is a free pet-project that can convert your favorite Youtube videos into MP3 files</p>
            <h1>How does it work?</h1>
            <p>This web application can convert any videos (specifically music videos) into regular MP3 files.</p>
            <h1>I'm receiving error: Invalid Video ID</h1>
            <p>Make sure to copy the actual Video ID (which goes after /watch?v=) instead of full URL.</p>
            <h1>What about the audio quality?</h1>
            <p>The output file is limited to 128kbps</p>
            <h1>Is it free to convert the files?</h1>
            <p>Yes, it is free, but you can download only 50 files per day. </p>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>